Dependencies:
imagemagick, glut

Change "numstages 25" in train.sh to alter sensitivity.
20 has many false positives and runs quickly
30 has many false negatives and takes a while
flower25.xml and flower30.xml are provided since they take a while to make

glFlower controls:
<w,a,s,d> ---------- displace picture
<mouse button> ----- displace picture by mouse movement
<-,=/+> ------------ Zoom In/Out
<esc> -------------- quit

Correct order to see results:
./unix_compile.sh
./manifest.sh
./train.sh Note that this step may take a very long time depending on configuration.
./flower samples/IMG_1997.jpg
